  "steps": [
    "Roughly chop tomatoes.",
    "Heat oil in a pan, add ginger, garlic, curry leaves and dried red chillies, mix and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add tomatoes, mix and saute for 4-5 minutes on medium heat.",
    "Add salt, sugar and ½ cup water and mix well. Cover and cook on medium heat for 5-6 minutes more. Allow to cool completely.",
    "Transfer the cooled mixture into a grinder jar. Add coconut and grind to fine paste. Transfer this paste into a bowl.",
    "To make tempering, heat oil in a pan, add split skinless black gram and mustard seeds and once they start to splutter, add asafoetida and curry leaves and sauté for a few seconds.",
    "Add this to ground chutney in the bowl and mix well. Transfer into a serving bowl and serve."
